    "We downloaded the initial NELA corpora from the Harvard Dataverse, under a CC0 1.0 license foot_14.",
    "The corpora have since been de-accessioned, and can longer be downloaded.",
    "We expand on this in Section 10.1.",
    "As a first processing step, we relabelled all publishers.",
    "This was done to 1) attribute articles to their original publisher (where possible), 2) ensure publisher information was up-to-date (MBFC had expanded their catalogue considerably) and 3) to mitigate the effects of publishers that might interfere with the learning signal."
